Package trainSet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Database
    The Database class provides the interface to query the SQLite database.
    FileManager
    The class 'FileManager' offers an interface for communication between the implementation logic with the database and the graphic part.
    Listener
    Superclass of listener that implementing the TableModelListener class provides methods for managing events generated by graphic elements to which that listener is connected
    Main
    The Main Class initializes the graphic interface and creates the objects to carry out the operations needed for the application to work.
    Model
    The Model class provides a representation for each file type Used in the software (those specified in the source file "FileType.java")
    OpenFile
    The class OpenFile stores the needed information about the user selection and manages the graphic element JFileChooser instantiating and displaying it to the user. .
    ResultContainer
    The class ResultContainer provides an interface to close the objects PreparedStatement and ResultSet after using them to query the database.
    TrainSetListener
    TrainSetListener Class, extends Listener (see Listener)"
    Window
    The Window Class manages the GUI with which the user can interact Allows you to select, add, and remove a train set.
